{"tid":1475782,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"港共政府最驚係咩？","createTime":"2019-08-15T14:58:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T15:00:24.000Z","uid":263326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"210d148a248fb78832cf23e9899e87c9844cc9c3","tid":1475782,"uid":263326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:58:13.000Z","msg":"除咗革命嘅苗頭<br />\n<br />\n就係管治唔到我地香港人<br />\n<br />\n如果依家既勢頭帶到落去立法會復會等等 <br />\n政府勢必換人 回應訴求<br />\n就算換咗人冇分別 只要我哋keep住呢個勢<br />\n最少我哋有希望爭取到雙普選<br />\n<br />\n所以大家唔好放棄<br />\n唔好分化 唔好割蓆<br />\n記住兄弟爬山各自努力<br />\n和理非 勇武 各有各做<br />\n<br />\n不捉鬼 不打鬼<br />\n勇武和理針對政權 針對警察 針對五大訴求<br />\n<br />\nKeep住呢團火 帶到落尾<br />\n去到最尾一齊除口罩啦好嫲？"},{"pid":"d018b71ab6ab2bff87254c639eeafaac23c5699c","tid":1475782,"uid":268213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:58:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5RGgS2w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5RGgS2w.jpg&h=da788c69&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RzinOAS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRzinOAS.jpg&h=d9d8f5a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a01c002f439ba4208ad0d3a11ec5930862f87389","tid":1475782,"uid":263326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:59:16.000Z","msg":"P  ush"},{"pid":"56d363f414d822d709c82df8d058b86ce2bc4d84","tid":1475782,"uid":263326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:59:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"627e4b722e5baff79d7dd46d50552a1617f048ab","tid":1475782,"uid":263326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:59:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"46f06733d6c42a07d037a52ae23b3956170bc241","tid":1475782,"uid":263326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:59:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6c180e9f84b171135f53b2d67055abef00675f22","tid":1475782,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:0